            "detail": 0,
            "format": 0,
            "mode": "normal",
            "style": "",
            "text": "Thanks to the car theft wave that’s swept over the nation, innocent people are being seriously hurt. Some people might think stealing another person’s ride isn’t a big deal, but a guy driving a stolen Dodge Challenger in St. Louis recently landed a mother and her 2-year-old son in the hospital.",
            "type": "text",
            "version": 1
          }
